INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (41,2,'2013-10-22 16:34:39','2013-10-22 16:34:39','<h1>CROWDSOURCED TECHNICAL EXPERTISE</h1>\n\n<p>Innovation.</p> \n\n<p>That\'s what we do, everyday.</p> \n\n<p>Our mission is to provide everyone with efficient access to the world\'s best technical talent, and to help reward the world\'s best designers, developers, and algorithmists for honing and proving their skills.</p>\n<h1>(1) DESIGN</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lets_create_it.png\" width=\"100%\"/><br /><strong>LET\'S CREATE IT</strong></p>\n<p>From mobile app screens, to UI for web and desktop apps, all the way through wireframes and prototypes, Design studio is where the path begins to build the visual representation of your innovative idea. More than just logos, this is true graphic and creative design, the front-end of technology innovation.</p> \n<p><em>Learn more about how <a href=\"/customers/what-we-do/case-studies/bryant-university\">Bryant University</a> is using Design Studio to drive creativity for their mobile applications.</em></p>\n<h1>(2) CLOUD DEVELOPMENT</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lets_build_it.png\" width=\"100%\"/><br /><strong>LET\'S BUILD IT</strong></p>\n<p>Let\'s build it - together - with the largest cloud-focused development community in the world. Cloud platforms have changed the way technology is delivered. We no longer need to run our own datacenters to access the computing power we require. We can pay for the compute resources we need, when we need them, and access the best resources regardless of where we are. The ubiquity of the internet and cloud computing platforms amongst the world\'s top technical resources means that there exists a \"distributed system\" of cloud experts all connected by the web. All you have to do is engage them.</p>\n<p><em>Learn more about how <a href=\"/customers/what-we-do/case-studies/nasa\">NASA</a> is building applications for the future of space exploration.</em></p>\n<h1>(2) ALGORITHMS & ANALYTICS</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/lets_solve_.png\" width=\"250px\"/><br /><strong>LET\'S SOLVE IT</strong>\n<br />This community contains hundreds of thousands of the best algorithmists and data scientists in the world. The crowdsourcing model puts the best minds for the task at hand in direct competition, ensuring that the best results rise to the top.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><em>Learn more about how <a href=\"/customers/what-we-do/case-studies/harvard\">Harvard Medical School</a> used crowdsourced data science - multiple experts competing at once - to vastly improved a legacy antibody sequencing algorithm\'s accuracy and speed from 4+ hours to 16 seconds.</em></p>\n\n<h1>REAL RESULTS</h1>\n<p>CloudSpokes works with leading enterprises, ISVs, and government agencies in search of talent and development resources:\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"/customers/what-we-do/case-studies\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/case-studies.png\" style=\"float-left;\" width=\"45%\"/></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/community/stories\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/community-stories.png\" style=\"float-left;\" width=\"45%\"/></a></p>','What We Do','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-autosave-v1','','','2013-10-22 16:34:39','2013-10-22 16:34:39','',10,'http://cloudspokes.wpengine.com/10-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
