INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (130,2,'2013-10-14 23:44:00','2013-10-15 03:44:00','<h1>Quickstart Guide</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Subscribe</strong>\r\nIn a timed development challenge, it only makes sense that the competitor that knows first will have an advantage. There\'s multiple ways to subscribe to CloudSpokes challenges and information. The most common are our <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/cloudspokes\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/cloudspokes\">Facebook</a>, <a href=\"http://www.cloudspokes.com/challenges.rss\">Challenges RSS</a>, and <a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Discuss</strong>\r\nWhether your intent for participating in these community challenges is to win cash, prove your skills, build your web resume, or learn something new, you\'ll be missing out on half of the experience if you don\'t engage your peers in this developer community. <a href=\"/how-it-works-members/collaborate\">Join the discussions</a> on any challenge you\'re interested in, find fellow active community members on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CloudSpokes/lists/cloudspokes-community\">Twitter</a>, or engage and ask questions on our <a href=\"/forums\">forums</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Profile</strong>\r\nAs a public platform, your <a href=\"http://www.cloudspokes.com/account/public-profile\">member profile</a> serves as a public testament of your skills and achievements. Take the time to complete some of the basic information so you receive all the due credit for your accomplishments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">For more information, visit our <a href=\"/help\" />Help Center >></a></p>\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/cVBOgM63XGE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>','Get Started','','publish','closed','closed','','get-started','','','2013-12-10 22:09:27','2013-12-11 03:09:27','',12991,'http://cloudspokes.wpengine.com/?page_id=130',0,'page','',0);
