INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (150,2,'2013-10-15 22:41:42','2013-10-16 02:41:42','<h1>AUTOMATED QUALITY AND SECURITY REVIEW</h1>\r\n<p>\"Thurgood\" is the codename for our proprietary toolset that provides automated build and testing of CloudSpokes challenge submissions. This service automates the process of testing and reviewing submitted code for quality, coverage, and other various coding standards. After queuing submissions based on platform/language, Thurgood taps into various services to deliver code review, including <a href=\"http://www.cloudbees.com\">Cloudbees</a>, <a href=\"http://www.checkmarx.com\">Checkmarx</a>, <a href=\"http://www.jslint.com\">JSLint</a>, <a href=\"http://phantomjs.org\">PhantomJS</a>, <a href=\"http://checkstyle.sourceforge.net\">Checkstyle</a>, and more. Documentation is tracked via&#160;<a href=\"https://papertrailapp.com\">Papertrail</a>.</p>\r\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/thurgood.png\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/thurgood.png\" width=\"100%\" /></a>\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/QlhFiZWxGFA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<h1>THURGOOD PROCESS</h1>\r\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/thurgood_submit.png\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/thurgood_submit_sm.png\" style=\"margin-right:10%;float-left;\" width=\"25%\"/></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/checkmarx_pdf.png\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/checkmarx_pdf_sm.png\" style=\"margin-right:10%;float-left;\" width=\"25%\"/></a><a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/papertrail.png\"><img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/papertrail_sm.png\" style=\"float-left;\" width=\"25%\"/></a>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"150px\">\r\n<h2>PROCESSING QUEUE</h2>\r\n<p>Submitted code enters the processing queue. All CloudSpokes packages reside in Cloud Storage until retrieved. Type-specific processing begins for the package, and the proper testing platform is reserved. Thurgood then unzips the code and generates testing platform build files.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"150px\">\r\n<h2>SECURITY SCAN</h2>\r\n<p>Once processed, the code and build files from the submitted package are then commited to a git repo. Cloudbees (Jenkins) kicks off the build process by downloading the code and running Checkmarx security and static analysis scans. This is all language-specific to the package.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"150px\">\r\n<h2>RESULTS LOG</h2>\r\n<p>Results from all scans and analysis are created via Papertrail and stored in Cloud Storage. This generates a PDF and returns a version to the participant\'s challenge-specific log account. Documentation is available to all challenge members, reviewers, and sponsors.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Thurgood','','publish','closed','closed','','thurgood','','','2013-12-09 22:33:54','2013-12-10 03:33:54','',30,'http://cloudspokes.wpengine.com/?page_id=150',0,'page','',0);
