INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (195,2,'2013-10-18 22:20:35','2013-10-19 02:20:35','<h1>HIGHLIGHTS</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>UX Storyboard and UI Prototype completely revamped for the Universitys Dining Services Mobile Application in only 8 days\r\n</li>\r\n<li>App-A-Thon poster design contest completed in only 48 hours, delivering Bryant University multiple quality submissions</li>\r\n<li>In only 12 hours  from launch of competition until completion  the University was delivered a safety-awareness poster design that was immediately implementable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/bryant_university1.png\" />\r\n<h1>CHALLENGE</h1>\r\n<p>With tight budgets, compact and often University event-specific deadlines, and a seemingly endless back-log of work, Bryant University faces very traditional bandwidth challenges. Utilizing the TopCoder Studio design community, Bryant is able to effectively force-multiply their dedicated internal teams creative bandwidth to accomplish more in an expedited time frame.</p>\r\n<h1>SOLUTION</h1>\r\n<p>Bryant University has found success in launching smaller, design focused projects through the TopCoder Studio community. This enables their team to effectively budget and manage a larger portfolio of creative projects. Studio design outputs, born from TopCoder competitions do not replace the work of their small and capable team, but rather augment their capability by bolstering the sheer volume of quality and creative work they can accomplish for thousands of dollars less than a traditional creative-services alternative.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The redesigned Dining Services Mobile Application allowed Bryant to put an emphasis on dietary information in a clear and concise manner  a value add to both the University and the growing, health-aware student population.</li>\r\n<li>Studio design contests created assets that can be used immediately, as well as providing icons, logos, designs, copy layouts and more that can be re-purposed for future projects.</li>\r\n<li>Bryant Universitys internal team gained crucial experience preparing, launching, managing, and completing Open Innovation & Crowdsourced competitions in a low-risk environment, paving the way for future projects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>','Bryant University','','publish','closed','closed','','bryant-university','','','2013-12-09 22:33:16','2013-12-10 03:33:16','',11,'http://cloudspokes.wpengine.com/?page_id=195',99,'page','',0);
