INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (264,5,'2008-12-18 18:14:43','2008-12-18 22:14:43','<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/?p=98\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-99 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/lmfeatured.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"462\" height=\"116\" /></a></p>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.local-motors.com/\">Local Motors</a> is an exciting new client which bills itself as a next generation American car company; \"the first disruptive entrant in the US automotive industry in decades and the first of its kind.\"\n\nThe company is on a mission to design, manufacture, and bring to market innovative, safer, more functional, lightweight, efficient cars through a revolutionary, local assembly and retail experience.\n\nDesign of Local Motors vehicles is done through its online community, and the company has come to the TopCoder Community to redesign and rebuild its website. The first competitions have just ended, a Studio <a href=\"http://studio.topcoder.com/?module=ViewContestDetails&amp;ct=2452\">mini-tournament</a> for <a href=\"http://studio.topcoder.com/?module=ViewSubmissions&amp;ct=2452\">storyboards</a> of the Local Motors homepage.\n\n<!--more-->The two-round mini-tournament structure gives both the client and the designers the best chance for success. With five $100 first round prizes, designers had the incentive to submit a quality design early to win in the first round and have a better chance for the $1000 tournament Grand Prize. The client was able to see designs from the TopCoder Community, then provide feedback and suggest changes midstream for the competitors to take under consideration for their final submission.\n\nEach designer can see the feedback left for his/her design as well as the feedback provided for the other four first-round winners, thus giving them the opportunity to rework their designs based on a full understanding of what the client was ultimately seeking.\n\nAs can be seen in the following examples, with quality <a href=\"http://studio.topcoder.com/forums?module=ThreadList&amp;forumID=571\">feedback</a> provided by the client, the designers made substantial improvements and enhancements to their designs. The end result was not only more developed submissions for the client to choose from, but designs that are ready for the next phase of competition: the prototyping phase.\n\n<strong>Winning Designer: srinivasc</strong>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15211.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-128 alignnone\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15211.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"507\" height=\"460\" /></a>\n\n<strong>2nd Place Designer: grandee</strong>\n\n<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15310.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-147\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15310.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"507\" height=\"309\" /></a>\n\nDesigner: djackmania\n\n<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15312.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-131\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15312.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"507\" height=\"343\" /></a>\n\nDesigner: leben\n\n<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15337.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-130\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15337.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"489\" height=\"507\" /></a>\n\nDesigner: srinivasc\n\n<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15276.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-129\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/15276.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"507\" height=\"465\" /></a>','Featured Client: Local Motors','Local Motors is an exciting new client which bills itself as a next generation American car company; \"the first disruptive entrant in the US automotive industry in decades and the first of its kind.\"','publish','open','open','','featured-client-local-motors','','','2008-12-18 18:14:43','2008-12-18 22:14:43','',0,'http://www.topcoder.com/direct/blogs/?p=98',0,'post','',0);
