INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (8625,5,'2011-11-14 22:09:54','2011-11-14 22:09:54','When you start working with the TopCoder Platform and you begin to engage the community, you quickly realize that you\'ve significantly expanded the number of people that are participating in your product development efforts.  I am responsible for TopCoder\'s product development, which also makes me a direct customer of our own platform.  Yes, we\'re building the TopCoder Platform using the TopCoder Platform.   I\'ll save all of the fun discussion around how effective this can be and how much control, flexibility, leverage and innovation power it gives you for a separate post or maybe a webinar (hint, hint).  Here are some fun stats pertaining to the portion of the TopCoder Community that has participated in TopCoder\'s own product development since the beginning of the year.\n\n<img title=\"Participation Stats\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/Screenshot_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"218\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Start ramping up <a href=\"https://www.topcoder.com/direct\" target=\"_blank\">your community</a> too.</span>','Do you have a community?','','publish','open','open','','do-you-have-a-community','','','2013-12-03 23:28:08','2013-12-04 04:28:08','',0,'http://www.topcoder.com/?p=8625',0,'post','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (8679,5,'2011-12-02 21:57:57','2011-12-02 21:57:57','A new feature that allows users to quickly find what they are looking for was recently introduced in <a href=\"https://www.topcoder.com/direct/\" target=\"_blank\">Cockpit</a>. This feature allows you to quickly narrow down the data on your screen to what you are looking for. For example, if I want to see every contest that is currently in Review I could simply type \"review\" in the search box. Or if I only want to see projects for a particular account or in a specific status, then I can set the filter accordingly and see my results narrow in real-time.\n\nGive it a try and, as always, send any suggestions to <a href=\"mailto:support@topcoder.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@topcoder.com</a>.\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;\" title=\"Filters\" src=\"http://www.topcoder.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/cockpit_filter_panel.png\" alt=\"Filters\" width=\"972\" height=\"417\" />','Cockpit Filtering Panels','','publish','open','open','','cockpit-filtering-panels','','','2013-12-03 23:28:08','2013-12-04 04:28:08','',0,'http://www.topcoder.com/?p=8679',0,'post','',0);
