INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (12568,5,'2012-08-01 15:59:35','2012-08-01 15:59:35','<div id=\"eoiWrapper\">\n<div class=\"row1\">\n<div class=\"rowInner\">\n<div class=\"block\">\n<div class=\"whatistc subBlock\">\n<h3><a class=\"jumper\" href=\"whatistc\">What is TopCoder?</a></h3>\nWe are a community of more than 415,000 software developers, algorithmists, and digital designers.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block\">\n<div class=\"whatiseoit subBlock\">\n<h3><a class=\"jumper\" href=\"whatiseoi\">What is EOI?</a></h3>\nEnterprise Open Innovation (EOI) is a fundamental shift in how you\n\napproach work, productivity and innovation.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"block blockLast\">\n<div class=\"whatcanido subBlock\">\n<h3><a class=\"jumper\" href=\"whatcanido\">What Can I Do?</a></h3>\nOn the TopCoder Platform you will approach work, productivity and innovation in an entirely new way. You will succeed like never before.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"whatistc normalBlock\">\n<div class=\"rightPos\">\n<div class=\"css\">Which global enterprises are succeeding on the TopCoder Platform? <a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/beta/case-studies\">Find out</a></div>\n<p class=\"content\">We are a community of more than 415,000 software developers, algorithmists, and digital designers. The community is accessed via the TopCoder Platform, which is the most advanced and sophisticated productivity and innovation platform in the world.</p>\n\n<h4>What do we do?</h4>\nFor our clients, who are Fortune 1000 enterprises and government agencies, we host specialized Open Innovation competitions, contests, and challenges and deliver back amazing software, design, and analytics solutions.\n<p class=\"content\">Now the real question: <a class=\"red jumper\" style=\"color: red;\" href=\"whatcanido\">What can TopCoder do for you?</a></p>\n\n</div>\n<h2><a class=\"jump whatistcjump\" name=\"whatistc\" href=\"#\"></a>What is TopCoder?</h2>\n<div class=\"imgWrappers\">\n<div>Image Holder</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"howdoesitwork normalBlock\">\n<div class=\"rightPos\">\n<div class=\"imgWrappers\">\n<div>Image Holder</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>How Does it Work?</h2>\n<p class=\"enormal\">At TopCoder, everything is a competition. Your projects are broken into the atomized pieces of work that comprise the entire build. By launching smaller competitions, hyper-specialists from within our community register, compete, and submit innovative solutions for you. You get the best talent working on the aspects of your projects they have exceptional skill in, on demand.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Access to specialized talent combined with a rigorous, standards-based competition methodology  This is Enterprise Open Innovation on the TopCoder Platform.</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"subtitle\">How Does it Scale?</h2>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Managing Open Innovation competitions can be just as difficult as managing a traditional workforce, so TopCoder created Copilots and they are your key to achieving scale like never before.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Copilots are an elite pool of TopCoder Community members who have proven to be exceptional technical managers of TopCoder competitions. They manage the technical aspects of crafting, launching, and managing competitions all the way through successful delivery. Copilots even manage updates, maintenance and Bug Races for you. They do this technical heavy lifting so you dont have to.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">What do you do? You orchestrate, you provide guidance, feedback and you set entire projects in motion.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">TopCoder atomizes your projects. Copilots technically manage the competitions that comprise the project, delivering you back incredible assets. You achieve more in parallel than you ever thought possible.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Re-think how you innovate.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"whatiseoi normalBlock\">\n<div class=\"rightPos\">\n<p class=\"whatiseoifirst\">Enterprise Open Innovation (EOI) is a fundamental shift in how you approach work, productivity and innovation. Today, you have access to talent from around the globe; talent with exceptional and specific skills.</p>\nWhen that talent, in the form of a competitive and collaborative community, is paired with a mature Open Innovation platform that is geared to handle the complexities of your enterprise, the outputs that emerge are exceptional, brought to market faster and on less spend.\n\nWhen you can innovate faster, when you can innovate continuously, and do so while lowering your risk, you will succeed.\n\nToday you have this access. This platform exists and as you read this, people like yourself, from Global 1000 enterprises are launching competitions on TopCoder that will help them succeed.\n\nYou have a lot to get done. Enterprise Open Innovation is your way forward.\n<p class=\"content\">You have a lot to get done. Enterprise Open Innovation is your way forward.</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n<h2><a class=\"jump whatiseoijump\" name=\"whatiseoi\" href=\"#\"></a>What is Enterprise Open Innovation?</h2>\n<div class=\"imgWrappers\">\n<div>Image Holder</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"whydo normalBlock\">\n<h2>Why do I need it?</h2>\n<p class=\"enormal\">The pace of technology and innovation is incredible and seemingly only accelerating. Coupled with this break-neck pace is the fragmentation of technologies and with it the specific skills required to effectively innovate. Then theres you. You need to get things done. You need to find ways to create value in new technologies while reducing your risk. You need to emerge as a problem solver for your enterprise in order to succeed.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">This is what TopCoder provides to you.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Through specialized competitions and powered by the worlds largest competitive community of software developers, algorithmists, and digital designers, we deliver amazing assets to you and your enterprise.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Why do you need TopCoder? Because starting right now, this is how you succeed.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"whatcanido normalBlock\">\n<h2><a class=\"jump whatcanidojump\" name=\"whatcanido\" href=\"#\"></a>What Can I Do?</h2>\n<p class=\"enormal\">On the TopCoder Platform you will approach work, productivity and innovation in an entirely new way. You will succeed like never before.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">The TopCoder Community of well over 415,000 members is comprised of the worlds best software developers, algorithmists, and digital designers. The capabilities within the community are representative of the three main pillars of work and innovation you can get accomplished on the TopCoder Platform.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">You will have assets created throughout the entire digital life-cycle. From the very front-end of innovation, into all phases of software development and continued through maintenance, updates, and security of the created assets, you will see more options, test more solutions, and bring more valuable assets to market faster, and on less spend.</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"subtitle\">Ultimate Flexibility in the Digital Life-Cycle</h2>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Through TopCoder you can bring an asset from the very front-end of innovation  an idea contest  all the way through maintenance of the finished digital product. However, most often you wont need to utilize the entire spectrum of competitions on a singular project. Your needs, from project to project can and will change.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">In one moment youll want to access specialized mobile UI designers and developers to bring a pre-existing idea quickly through rapid-prototyping. In the next moment, you might have a need to only build software components for a highly defined, language specific build. In parallel and for a completely different project, its quite likely you may have an algorithm you need optimized to handle a data set that is growing at an exponential rate.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Through the TopCoder Platform, you get the outputs of your projects you need, when you need them. Its nice to know the entire life-cycle is at your fingertips, but its important to realize the flexibility you attain by working with the TopCoder Community.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"normalBlock\">\n<h2 class=\"noindent subtitle\">The 3 Pillars of the Digital Life-Cycle:</h2>\n<h2 class=\"noindent\">Front-End Innovation, Software Development, and Algorithms &amp; Analytics</h2>\n<div class=\"detailEoi\">\n\n<img style=\"margin-top: 15px;\" src=\"../wp-content/themes/tc-eoi-theme/i/eoi/g4.png%20\" alt=\"\" />\n<div class=\"detailBlock\">\n<h4 class=\"blue\">Front-End Innovation</h4>\nOften referred to as FEI, this is where you bring new value to your organization. From the very beginning of innovation  the raw idea  all the way through rapid-prototyping, how you approach your FEI is crucial to how you ultimately innovate and bring value to your end-users.\n\nOn the TopCoder Platform your FEI will be ignited. Ideas, concepts, storyboards, interfaces, prototypes and more will be delivered to you. And because each phase is its own unique competition, you will receive multiple looks and feels, so the toughest part might just be choosing your winning submissions.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"detailBlock\">\n<h4 class=\"green\">Software Development</h4>\nSoftware makes the business world go. As markets shift and software continues to permeate all walks of life, you need a repeatable process to bring quality software solutions to market.\n\nDeveloping software through the TopCoder Platform garners you uncompromised quality, predictability and scale. Languages and technology preferences will change, but the way you access hyperspecialized technological talent will remain constant.\n\nEvery asset, every line of code will be built to your exacting IT standards and expertly documented so building out updates and maintaining your solutions becomes easier and takes less time.\n\nRemember, you are delivered the winning submissions, at a pre-defined budget, within a structured time frame. You save time, money, and the code quality is unsurpassed.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"detailBlock lastBlock\">\n<h4 class=\"orange\">Algorithms &amp; Analytics</h4>\nIn this burgeoning era of Big Data, there is an ever increasing need to deliver illuminating analytics that help your enterprise navigate markets more and create value from data more effectively. But often the data is overwhelming, and your enterprise is ill-equipped, from both a talent and innovation stand point, to utilize this data in effective and purposeful ways. Ways that deliver your enterprise a big market advantage.\n\nBut what if how you approach value creation in analytics could be far simpler and could lead to extreme value outcomes that elevate your enterprise above your competitors? What if every time you wanted to optimize an algorithm, better understand your data, discover buried correlations in the data, or solve a complex data-driven challenge you simply dialed-up a contest? What if that contest attracted hundreds of the worlds top algorithmists to your challenge who in-turn submit innovative data solutions for your enterprise?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"edlc\" class=\"normalBlock tedl\">\n<h2>The Entire Digital Life-Cycle</h2>\n<p class=\"enormal\">Today, through an advanced and nuanced platform developed for your enterprise and powered by the worlds largest community of competitive developers, algorithmists, and digital designers, the entire digital life-cycle is at your fingertips. All assets and solutions delivered through standardized and highly scalable processes, where you receive and pay only for the best outputs, born from specialized competitions.</p>\n<p class=\"enormal\">You are being asked to find a new way forward in technology, productivity, and innovation. You need to find a way to take more swings and do so at greatly reduced risk. The TopCoder Platform, powered by the TopCoder Community is your solution to success.</p>\n<p class=\"content\"></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"bottomBlock\">\n<div class=\"rowInner\">\n<h1>How would you like to learn more?</h1>\n<div class=\"detailBlocks\"><a class=\"like\" href=\"http://connect.topcoder.com/how-can-we-help.html?utm_campaign=homepagelink\">Id like to talk with TopCoder</a></div>\n<div class=\"detailBlocks css\">\n\nWhich global enterprises are succeeding on the TopCoder Platform?\n\n<a href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/beta/case-studies\">Find out</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"detailBlocks video\"><span class=\"youtube\"><iframe title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/x5uSceQrirw?wmode=transparent&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;iv_load_policy=3&amp;showsearch=0&amp;rel=1&amp;theme=dark\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"271\" height=\"138\"></iframe></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','Enterprise open Innovation','','trash','open','closed','','whatiseoi','','','2013-12-10 22:06:53','2013-12-11 03:06:53','',0,'http://localhost/reviewer/tchome-eoi/?page_id=12568',0,'page','',0);
