INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (12838,5,'2011-03-11 12:36:19','2011-03-11 12:36:19','<h2>TopCoder\'s History</h2>\nTopCoder, Inc.started in 2001 as a series of programming competitions and community interested in algorithms and software development. Initially, these competitions were purely for fun and prizes and to establish skill level within various programming disciplines. The modelsoon went viral within the U.S. technical university system and became international even more quickly. The model was expanded to includecommercial software development competitions predominately in newer technology paradigms  Java/.NET, object oriented programming, component based development and heavy algorithm emphasis. Today, TopCoderhosts a growing list of Fortune 500 and some of the largest tech companies as clients and a community base of 300,000 members worldwide.\n\n<h2>Evolution</h2>\n2001 - Company founded, first single round match','History','','trash','closed','closed','','overview','','','2013-12-10 22:02:21','2013-12-11 03:02:21','',231,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=25',0,'page','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (12839,5,'2011-03-11 12:33:01','2011-03-11 12:33:01','<p>\nJoin the TopCoder Community and unlock the world\'s largest community of software engineers, computer scientists, and digital creators. The TopCoder Platform lets you use <a href=\"/how-it-works/sdlc/#competitionListing\" class=\"big\">a wide range of competitions</a> and move from a traditional staffing approach to a <a href=\"/how-it-works/virtualfactory\" class=\"big\">virtual factory</a> model. Focus on your business, <strong>stop worrying about hours and start driving results.</strong>\n\nSee some of the <a class=\"big\" href=\"/who-uses-topcoder\">enterprises and government agencies</a> using TopCoder.\n</p>\n<h2>What kinds of projects can I do with TopCoder?</h2>\n<p>\nCustomers come to TopCoder with a wide range of projects to complete.\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Mobile Applications</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Analytics and Optimization</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Scientific Algorithm Development</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Online Communities</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Open Platforms</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Digital Media</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>Business Systems</strong></li>\n</ul>\nDidn\'t see what you were looking for? Set up a <a href=\"http://info.topcoder.com/request-a-free-consult/\" class=\"big\">free consultation</a> to review your specific project and determine how we can work together. Or find out more about <a class=\"big\" href=\"/how-it-works\">how projects work</a> on our platform.\n\n<h2>Licensing for Enterprise Programs</h2>\nWhether you already know what you want to build or if you need help figuring it out, TopCoder can customize a program to fit your unique business needs. During pre-sales consultation our specialists will work with you to understand your needs and tailor an engagement strategy, including how to get started, roll out, and ramp up your program.\n\nAll Enterprise Licenses include:\n<ul>\n	<li>Initial training and on-boarding support.</li>\n	<li>Unlimited ability to run software, algorithm, and studio (creative) competitions.</li>\n	<li>Ongoing support and program level consultation to help you maximize your investment.</li>\n	<li>Hosting and management of to a TopCoder network community site.</li>\n	<li>Unlimited usage of TopCoder\'s extensive digital asset catalog of over 1,500 software components.</li>\n</ul>\n\nYou can find out <a href=\"/aboutus\" class=\"big\">more about TopCoder</a> or get started today with a <a href=\"http://info.topcoder.com/request-a-free-consult/\" class=\"big\">free consultation</a>.','Digital Innovation and Software Product Development Powered by The World\'s Largest Development Community','','publish','closed','closed','','solutions','','','2011-03-11 12:33:01','2011-03-11 12:33:01','',0,'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (12840,5,'2011-03-11 12:33:11','2011-03-11 12:33:11','Our customers utilize the TopCoder platform for accessing the world\'s elite talent for digital asset creation. When you engage with TopCoder you are not only getting access to our cutting edge platform for creating, building and analyzing - you are also becoming part of our elite community.\n<h2>Our Community is Your Community</h2>\nFirst and foremost, TopCoder is a community. With a global membership of digital professionals and a large and growing clientele, TopCoder represents an entirely new way to get things done. Whether youre building an entire digital strategy, creating a web site, mobile app, internal application, or trying to make sense of your data  tapping into the TopCoder community will open up opportunities that simply weren\'t possible before. From thinking of an idea to making it real, TopCoder can help you with most anything digital. One important thing: as you begin to engage with our community, something funny happens you become part of it.\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a class=\"big\" href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/wp-content/themes/TopCoder-Home/sampleprojects/1/index.html\">Take a tour</a> of the deliverables for a completed project. This project was run to build a <a class=\"big\" href=\"./copilots\">copilot</a> capability, which allows customers to use community members to support the projects they are running on TopCoder.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"></p>\n\n<div class=\"mceTemp mceIEcenter\" style=\"text-align: left\"><dl> <dt><a class=\"big\" href=\"http://www.topcoder.com/wp-content/themes/TopCoder-Home/sampleprojects/1/index.html\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-7736 \" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/screen_concept.gif\" alt=\"Click to view project example\" width=\"408\" height=\"304\" /></a></dt> <dd>Click image for project tour! </dd> </dl></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>\n','How Does It Work?','','trash','closed','closed','