INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (13072,3,'2013-12-03 22:41:57','2013-12-04 03:41:57','[table]\r\n\\\\TopCoder Platform Specialist ~~ Have a specific question about operating the platform? Have no fear; our Platform Specialists are here for you! They are your virtual go-to resource, masters of operating the platform, and they are at the ready to answer your questions and help you learn, grow, and scale Open Innovation on the TopCoder Platform. ||V||V||V\r\n\r\n\\\\TopCoder University Master\'s Pass ~~ We think its a great thing to keep learning, so we created TCU or TopCoder University to help you do exactly that. Video tutorials, educational webinars, platform enhancements &amp; updates, best practices tips and much more are all at your fingertips 24-7-365. This is your Masters Pass to help you master Open Innovation on the TopCoder Platform. ||V||V||V\r\n\r\n\\\\Advanced Analytics &amp; Reporting~~ The TopCoder Platform comes pre-loaded with a robust analytics and reporting capability. From your beautifully visualized enterprise productivity dashboard to per contest market analysis, youll know exactly how productive you are being on the platform, how much each unit of work is actually costing you, and much more! This makes it easy to track and to internally share your productivity on the TopCoder Platform. ||V||V||V\r\n\r\n\\\\Free Get Going Gameplan~~ This is your opportunity to hit the ground running on the TopCoder Platform. Gameplans on TopCoder are documents showcasing for you the budget &amp; timeline and all the contests that comprise your specific project. Youll see your path to success laid-out before you and this first Get Going Gameplan is free! So, get going on the TopCoder Platform. ||V||V||V\r\n\r\n\\\\Deep Dive Domain Training ~~ On the TopCoder Platform you can create assets in 3 main pillars of digital creation. They are: Front-end Design (with a focus on UI/UX innovation), Software Development, and Big Data Algorithms &amp; Analytics. You have access to a web-based, hour long, personalized deep dive session with a TopCoder domain expert in each of the 3 pillars. Understand what you want to create and access\r\nour expertise to help you get it done on the TopCoder Platform. ||Choose 1||All 3||All 3\r\n\r\n\\\\Customer Roundtable Attendee ~~ The TopCoder CRT or Customer Roundtable is our semi-annual gathering of TopCoder Platformers. These are the folks, just like you, who are actively managing competitions on the platform. The gathering focuses on showcasing best practices, platform enhancements, and learning from your fellow peers who are growing and scaling Open Innovation on the TopCoder Platform. ||X||V||V\r\n\r\n\\\\On-Site Training ~~ Want on-site training? You got it. Well first discuss your goals and bring a training program to you that reflects your current pipeline of work and gets you well situated for the future projects you have in mind. We understand you may want this higher-touch for you and your team. We want you to be as successful as possible on the TopCoder Platform.<em>**Training is subject to scheduling and availability. Non-Enterprise clients, please inquire about pricing</em>||X||Available||V\r\n\r\n\\\\Expert Services ~~ Need just in time training for a new initiative? Its yours. Have specific technology needs and want TopCoder to prepare our community to meet them with you? Lets do it. Require field support to respond to an escalated and timely issue? As an enterprise client, you get it all on the TopCoder Platform. ||Available||Available||Available\r\n\r\n\\\\Unlimited Seats ~~ Are you looking to scale Open Innovation for an entire division of your enterprise? Great! Maybe you have even bigger goals and want the TopCoder Platform in every one of your divisions? Even better! As an enterprise client, you can scale your Open Innovation success as far and wide as you wish with no limits to how many seats you can access on the TopCoder Platform. ||X||X||V\r\n\r\n[/table]','Pricing','','publish','closed','closed','','pricing','','','2013-12-03 22:43:20','2013-12-04 03:43:20','',0,'http://cloudspokes.wpengine.com/?page_id=13072',0,'page','',0);
